# `evo-sdk-gen` from evo-core-eng writes its per-language outputs
# to `./sdks/` relative to the invoking cwd. Stray runs from this
# tree should not pollute the repo; ignore them symmetrically with
# evo-core-eng's own /sdks/ rule. The shell vendoring path lives
# in evo-ui-eng/apps/evo-ui-shell/src/sdk/ and tracks a deliberate
# snapshot.
/sdks/

# AI tooling — never committed.
#
# Excludes per-machine settings, project memories, caches, and
# rule files for every coding-assistant tool. Two concerns:
# (1) per-user / per-machine settings (allowlists, model
# preferences, auth state) leaking into the public repo, and
# (2) project-memory files containing internal context.
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
.cursor/
.cursorrules
.cursorignore
.aider*
.aiderignore
.continue/
.windsurf/
.windsurfrules
.codeium/
.zed/
.junie/
.github/copilot-instructions.md
